Your Score: moderate Depression.
depression could be what’s stopped you working or studying, meeting friends, or doing the things that make you happy.
This isn’t a diagnosis but it looks like it’s time to get help, and get your life back (as hard as that might sound right now).
Lots of people who experience depression have got through it by talking with someone who’s trained to help.
